    .guide
        .container
            .guide__title(data-translate="guideTitle") How to get  #[span.magenta free spins?]
            .guide__list
                .guide__item
                    .guide__item-num 1
                    .guide__item-text(data-translate="guideItemText1") #[span.green-txt MAKE] a deposit from ₴150 using the #[strong «Profiplay» ] payment card.
