                summary(data-translate="prizeDropBtn") Prize distribution
                .drop-txt
                    .drop-txt-list(data-translate="prizeDrop")
                        p #[span.list-num 1] Make a deposit of at least ₴150 exclusively using the digital "Profiplay" card.
                        p #[span.list-num 2] After making a deposit with the aforementioned card, you will automatically qualify for a bonus in the form of FS in the game “Starlight Princess” from the Provider Pragmatic Play. The bonus is credited with a wagering requirement of ₴150 for deposits ranging from ₴150 to ₴249, ₴250 for deposits from ₴250 to ₴599, and ₴600 for deposits of ₴600 and above.  To receive the bonus, you must place bets in the "Casino" section totaling at least ₴150.
